#. type: Content of: <chapter><title>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:6
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Einleitungstext"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:8
msgid ""
"With the <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ you can "
"enjoy all benefits of professional services and exclusive Business Features "
"offered by the OTRS Group. Optimize your internal &amp; external "
"communication for more service quality – flexibly adjustable to your "
"operating scenario."
msgstr "Mit der <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ können Sie alle Vorteile der professionellen Dienstleistungen und exklusiven Business-Funktionen, die durch die OTRS-Gruppe angeboten werden, genießen. Optimieren Sie Ihre interne &amp; externe Kommunikation für mehr Servicequalität - flexibel auf Ihr Betriebsszenario anpassbar."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:11
msgid ""
"The sleek and fast framework of OTRS 6 is the base for the <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-improving-customer-"
"service/\"><emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business "
"Solution</emphasis>™</ulink>.  On top are available for you additionally an "
"exclusive set of features. These include the <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-improving-customer-service"
"/#OTRS-Business-Solution-Cloud-Services\">integrated Cloud Services</ulink> "
"of the <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ that you "
"can flexibly activate or deactivate according to your deployment scenarios."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/introduction.xml:17
msgid ""
"Additionally you have the choice between 3, 7 or an unlimited number of "
"various <ulink url=\"https://www.otrs.com/otrs-business-solution-improving-"
"customer-service/#OTRS-Business-Solution-Cloud-Services\">freely selectable "
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™ Features</ulink> "
"- depending on you contract level.  Profit also from regular, free updates, "
"the best OTRS security and support as well as installation and configuration"
" carried out by our consultants."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><title>
#: en/content/upgrading.xml:6
msgid "Upgrading to <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™"
msgstr "Installation der <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business Solution</emphasis>™"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><para>
#: en/content/upgrading.xml:8
msgid ""
"In order to upgrade to <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS Business "
"Solution</emphasis>™, you need a valid contract with the OTRS group. If you "
"already have a contract, you can upgrade to <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS "
"Business Solution</emphasis>™ by visiting the <emphasis role=\"bold\">OTRS "
"Business Solution</emphasis>™ administration screen in your OTRS instance. "
"You can find the link to this screen in the \"System Administration\" "
"section of the admin area of your OTRS Free instance. Please note that you "
"first have to register your system using the system registration mechanism."
msgstr ""

