#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-webservice.xml:18
msgid ""
"Normally when a field is changed in a screen (i.e. the ticket priority in "
"the New phone ticket screen) the values of other fields could be updated. "
"That is the case with this type of dynamic fields, as they could also "
"include all screen field values in the request and the remote server could "
"potentially return completely different values depending on input."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-webservice.xml:24
msgid ""
"Additionally if the dynamic field source object already exists (i.e. a "
"ticket, and the field is set in the Free Fields screen), the details of the "
"already created ticket are also included in the request."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/features/dynamicfield-webservice.xml:32
msgid ""
"To make this feature work it is necessary to have the following components:"
